		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It is a weak connection from the bonding of the side ribbon to the glass. Unfortunately, unlike the common vertical lines, an easy fix is not known for this one as that ribbon is quite delicate.<br /><br />Glad to see the &quot;bivert&quot; mod nitro2k01 and I made ages ago is still popular <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

